tt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="马耳他马特。图片来源：Vinca Petersen" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese.-Credit-Vinca-Petersen-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Matt-Maltese">马特·马耳他（Matt Maltese）</a>从即将发行的专辑“她的她”中分享了他渴望的新单曲《我的一生》。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/matt-maltese-interview-in-conversation-good-morning-its-now-tomorrow-3048883">我们从与Matt Maltese的对话视频聊天中学到的五件事</a></strong></li></ul><p>柔和，深情和浪漫的曲目使马耳他人承认他对伴侣的爱以及他向他们渴望了多少。 <em>“我摔倒在你的手中 /改变了世界 /挑战，意在想让你更多，”</em>他用平滑的低音线和美丽的钢琴布置唱歌。</p><p>在一份新闻稿中谈到曲目时，马耳他分享说：“可能是我在一首歌中所做的最大渴望。这首歌是一种真正的乐趣，这是一种真正的乐趣，并受到我与之成长的所有摩托车和灵魂的启发。我并不感到羞耻。我并不感到羞耻地说，我对通过大胆地通过《美国人的灵魂》宣告了大胆的爱情声明，这是我的情绪大致可悲的，这是美国人的灵魂音乐。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="为你一生" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jl9_6Q8cml0?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我的一生”为您提供了马耳他即将发行的第六张专辑“ Hers”的第三个品尝者，该专辑定于5月16日通过The Orchard发行（<a href="https://mattmaltese.orcd.co/hers" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>预订/预先保存）。该曲目遵循先前发布的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/matt-maltese-returns-with-wistful-single-anytime-anyplace-anyhow-listen-3831032">随时随地，任何地方，无论如何</a>”和“始终有MF”。</p><p> “她的”是马耳他第二张LP“ Krystal”以来的第一张完全自我制作的专辑。一份新闻稿分享说，这张专辑是他的“迄今为止最孤立，最亲密的”和“存在于暮光之城，将衷心的歌曲创作和干燥的智慧与柔和的弦乐，木管乐器的繁荣或吱吱作响的老钢琴配对。”</p><p>在谈到这张专辑时，马耳他分享道：“我写了很多来自痴迷的地方的音乐，但是这张唱片是写着长期爱情的反思。复杂性和奇妙的道路以及从中出现的更加知情的心痛。我真的很反思和奴隶……有点像一年来写一张非常重要的电子邮件。”</p><p>他继续说：“我足够英国人，以至于过去写很多情歌。也许纸上更有趣的事情是去世界的另一端，写一张有关史前史前生物或其他东西的概念专辑，但最终，我们都是人类，爱与人都在不断受到影响。我们都是我的工作。 </p><figure id="attachment_3847310" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847310" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847310" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="马特·马耳他的“她的”专辑插图。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-Hers-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847310" class="wp-caption-text">马特·马耳他的“她的”专辑插图。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>“她的”曲目列表是：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1。&#39;Arthouse Cinema&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>2。“公共汽车更换火车”</strong><br /> <strong>3。&#39;生日快乐&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>4。&#39;随时随地，无论如何&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>5。&#39;总是一些MF&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>6。“为空虚治愈”</strong><br /> <strong>7。“从你自己那里度假”</strong><br /> <strong>8。</strong><br /> <strong>9。“一尘不染的永恒黑暗”</strong><br /> <strong>10。“纠结”</strong><br /> <strong>11。“每个人都像我一样疯狂&#39;</strong></p><p>音乐家还宣布了在美国，欧洲和英国进行的标题巡回演出。您可以查看以下日期的完整列表，然后访问<a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fmatt-maltese-tickets%2Fartist%2F2315777" target="_blank" rel="noopener">此处</a>购买我们的门票，并<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fmatt-maltese-tickets%2Fartist%2F5211877" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买英国门票。 </p><figure id="attachment_3847312" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847312" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847312" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-2025-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="Matt Maltese 2025 Tour海报。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2331" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-2025-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-2025-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x466.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-2025-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x932.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-2025-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x811.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-2025-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1622.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Matt-Maltese-2025-tour-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1245.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847312" class="wp-caption-text"> Matt Maltese 2025 Tour海报。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>Matt Maltese的“为您巡回演出我的一生” 2025 US，英国和欧洲巡回演唱会是：</strong></h2><p><strong>九月</strong><br /><strong>16马拉松音乐作品，纳什维尔</strong><br /><strong>17会幕，亚特兰大</strong><br /><strong>19地下，夏洛特