 Radiohead 2025 Tour似乎已得到管理层的确认https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-2025-tour-semelly-semelly-confirmed-by-management-management-management-3847272?utm_source = rss＆source = rss＆utm_medium = radiom_campaign=radiohead-campaign=radiohead-2025-confrimn-confrirm-confrirm-confrirm-confrirm-confrirm-confirm-confirm-confirm-confirm-confirm-confirmAnagricel Duran Tue, 18 Mar 2025 18:07:36 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3847272 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Radiohead的汤姆·约克（Thom Yorke）在2017年的格拉斯顿伯里节（Glastonbury Festival）在金字塔舞台上演出。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>该消息是在乐队组建一个新法律实体的一周后发布的，表明他们可能会计划今年的重要活动</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-2025-tour-seemingly-confirmed-by-management-3847272">Radiohead 2025巡回演出似乎已得到管理层的确认，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Radiohead的汤姆·约克（Thom Yorke）在2017年的格拉斯顿伯里节（Glastonbury Festival）在金字塔舞台上演出。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Thom-Yorke-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>看来<a href="/artist/Radiohead">Radiohead的</a>管理层已经确认了今年乐队即将进行的一段时间。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-interview-colin-greenwood-how-to-disappear-photo-book-band-future-tour-3803426">科林·格林伍德（Colin Greenwood</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://ra.co/news/82380?fbclid=IwY2xjawJGX5RleHRuA2FlbQIxMQABHcjfNF2ZseTgQIXjeeewXj1Nzq3ha02wOpW5W0JJYhwnI6ViHBrC5jOsrQ_aem_lcZzYwy38x6VdeIqj2NOzg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《居民顾问》</em></a>报道，据称，该乐队的管理层（Blueyed Pictures）捐赠了四张“您选择的Radiohead音乐会”的门票，由乐队的管理层捐赠给了由Palisades High School举办的洛杉矶消防救济拍卖。</p><p>昨天（3月17日）关闭了火灾救济拍卖，门票的上市解释说，出价最高的人将能够选择其首选的城市和“根据乐队的巡回演出计划”。</p><p>该商店还报告说，Radiohead的密切消息人士已向他们确认，<a href="/artists/Thom-Yorke">汤姆·约克（Thom Yorke</a> and Co）“在今年秋天的一系列居住演出中都占据了欧洲城市的持有。”</p><p> Radiohead的最后一次现场表演是在2018年8月1日在费城的富国银行中心举行的，标志着他们的“月球形泳池”之旅的结束，以支持他们的<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/radiohead-a-moon-shaped-pool-talking-points-8462">同名专辑</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-suggest-upcoming-activity-by-forming-new-legal-entity-3846096">乐队组建一个新的法人实体</a>之后不久，有关Radiohead团聚日期可能确认的消息是，他们可能计划在2025年计划进行重大活动。 </p><figure id="attachment_3847296" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847296" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847296" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Radiohead-performing.jpg" alt="Radiohead在Coachella Valley Music and Arts Festival（周末2）的第一天在Coachella舞台上表演。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Radiohead-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Radiohead-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Radiohead-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Radiohead-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Radiohead-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Radiohead-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847296" class="wp-caption-text"> Radiohead在Coachella Valley Music and Arts Festival（周末2）的第一天在Coachella舞台上表演。</figcaption></figure><p>上周，乐队以Rheuk25的名字创建了有限的责任合伙企业（LLP），这是他们过去在专辑《 Tour或Reissue公告》之前几次所做的事情。</p><p> LLP允许Radiohead独立运营其业务事务，而无需依靠唱片公司和外部公司的框架。乐队没有关于法律举动可以表示的进一步信息。</p><p> Radiohead的所有五名成员 - 约克， <a href="/artists/Jonny-Greenwood">Jonny Greenwood，</a> <a href="/artists/Colin-Greenwood">Colin Greenwood</a> ， <a href="/artists/Ed-O-Brien">Ed O&#39;Brien</a>和<a href="/artists/Philip-Selway">Philip Selway</a> - 都被列为Rheuk25 LLP的官员。</p><p>自从2003年的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-7087-313618">冰雹到小偷</a>”之后，Radiohead与EMI/Parlophone分道扬ways以来一直独立运作。他们在2007年创立了Xurbia Xendless，然后通过其网站发布了开创性的“支付您想要的东西”格式的“<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-577-1352464">彩虹</a>”。该专辑和随后的发行版与XL录音合作以物理格式处理。</p><p>该乐队最近对他们的未来计划非常有责任。去年，约克（Yorke）成为头条新闻，说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thom-yorke-really-doesnt-give-a-fuck-if-you-want-radiohead-to-return-3804946">他“真的不给他妈的”，如果粉丝们希望Radiohead回来</a>。当澳大利亚媒体<a href="https://www.abc.net.au/news/2024-10-21/thom-yorke-the-smile-interview-cutouts-australian-solo-tour/104490320" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Double J</em></a>询问他对乐队未来的猜测的想法时，他回答说：“我不知道这一点，也不是真正的他妈的。” </p><figure id="attachment_3847298" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3847298" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3847298" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jonny-Greenwood-performing.jpg" alt="Radiohead的乔尼·格林伍德（Jonny Greenwood）于2017年7月4日在英格兰曼彻斯特（Manchester）在阿联酋老特拉福德（E​​mirates Old Trafford）演出。 （Andrew Benge/Redferns的照片）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jonny-Greenwood-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Jonny-Greenwood-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3847298" class="wp-caption-text"> Radiohead的乔尼·格林伍德（Jonny Greenwood）于2017年7月4日在英格兰曼彻斯特（Manchester）在阿联酋老特拉福德（E​​mirates Old Trafford）演出。 （Andrew Benge/Redferns的照片）</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说：“对任何人都没有冒犯，也没有犯错，感谢您的关心。” “但是我认为，我们已经获得了做对我们有意义的事情的权利，而不必解释自己或对其他人对我们应该做的事情的历史构想做出回应。”</p><p>这是在贝斯手科林·格林伍德（Colin Greenwood） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-interview-colin-greenwood-how-to-disappear-photo-book-band-future-tour-3803426">赶上<em>NME的</em></a>新照片书<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radioheads-colin-greenwood-announces-photo-book-of-life-with-the-band-how-to-disappear-3607539" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《如何消失》</em></a>之后，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-have-been-back-together-rehearsing-it-was-really-fun-3791835">在整个夏天对乐队的团圆排练开放。</a></p><p>科林当时说：“我们在夏天聚会了几天，只是跑了所有的歌曲，在2018年我们离开的地方捡起了。见到每个人真的很有趣。</p><p> “Beyond that, everyone&#39;s heads are focussed on finishing up what they&#39;ve been doing. <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-smile-cancel-tour-as-jonny-greenwood-recovers-from-intensive-care-stay-3774522">My brother has been unwell and is still recovering</a> . Rehearsals were really fun and amicable, though. We rehearsed in this studio called The Church where we ended up finishing up &#39;OK Computer&#39;, so the last time I was there was 1996 recording the bass for &#39;Airbag&#39;. There we were, back in Crouch End. It was great, but beyond that get together, I&#39;m当然，我们会聚在一起制定计划 - 但是我不知道。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Radiohead-住在圣保罗（2018年4月）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/T0uYhclh9f8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在此之前，他的兄弟<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jonny-greenwood-interview-the-smile-cutouts-radiohead-return-3801554" target="_blank" rel="noopener">乔尼（Jonny）与<em>NME</em>分享了</a>他发现彩排“有趣而自然”，但继续补充说，由于成员专注于“单个项目”，因此在2025年没有与Radiohead相关的任何计划。</p><p>在其他新闻中，Radiohead最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-share-new-playlist-of-the-bends-b-sides-and-remixes-to-mark-albums-30th-anniversary-3846967">分享了“ The Bends” B面和混音的播放列表，以庆祝专辑的30周年</a>。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-mark-the-bends-30th-anniversary-with-unseen-1995-live-show-video-3846446">乐队分享了一部看不见的现场视频之后，该播放列表的发行列表发行了，该视频是Yorke发行“ The Bends”之时的独奏节目之一</a>。</p><p>本月初，在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-pritchard-thom-yorke-announce-debut-album-tall-tales-with-eclectic-single-this-conversation-is-missing-your-voice-3845363">约克和马克·普里查德（Mark Pritchard）一起宣布了他们的第一张全长专辑</a>。 “ Tall Tales”将于5月9日通过Warp发行，其中包括单曲“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mark-pritchard-thom-yorke-announce-debut-album-tall-tales-with-eclectic-single-this-conversation-is-missing-your-voice-3845363">此对话错过您的声音</a>”和“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-thom-yorke-and-mark-pritchards-eerie-new-collab-back-in-the-game-on-warp-records-3837789">Back Back in the Game</a> ”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/radiohead-2025-tour-seemingly-confirmed-by-management-3847272">Radiohead 2025巡回演出似乎已得到管理层的确认，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 Gwyneth Paltrow认为TimothéeChalamet是“思想人的性别符号” https://www.nme.com/news/film/gwyneth-paltrow-believes-timothee-chalamet-is-the------------------------------ in-inking-mans-sex-syx-Symbol-3847291？ m_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = gwyneth-paltrow-believes-timothee-chalamet-is-is-thinking-mans-mans-sex-symbolVictoria Luxford Tue, 18 Mar 2025 17:05:54 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3847291 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格温妮丝·帕特洛（Gwyneth Paltrow）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他是一个真正认真对待自己的工作的人”</p><p>格温妮丝·帕特洛（Gwyneth Paltrow）认为，蒂莫西·查拉梅特（TimothéeChalamet）是<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/gwyneth-paltrow-believes-timothee-chalamet-is-the-thinking-mans-sex-symbol-3847291">“思想人的性别符号”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格温妮丝·帕特洛（Gwyneth Paltrow）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Timotheee-Chalamet-Gwyneth-Paltrow-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwyneth-paltrow">格温妮丝·帕特洛（Gwyneth Paltrow）</a>称赞了她的新联合主演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/timothee-chalamet">蒂莫西·查拉梅特（TimothéeChalamet）</a> ，称他为“有思想的人的性爱象征”。</p><p>乔什·萨夫迪（Josh Safdie）在接受<a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/story/gwyneth-paltrow-2025-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《名利场》（Vanity Fair）</em></a>的采访时，讨论了研究新的A24项目<em>马蒂·苏普莱姆（Marty Supreme）</em>的工作时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/safdie-brothers">乔什·萨菲（Josh Safdie）的</a>《 2019年<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/uncut-gems"><em>邪教组织</em></a>》（Cult）的随访。自2019年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avengers-endgame"><em>《复仇者联盟》（Avengers）以来就没有在大屏幕上出现：《残局》（Endgame）</em></a> ，她承认自己从电影中脱颖而出，从未看过<em>《未剪彩》</em>或任何Chalamet电影。</p><p>但是，与他一起工作后，她自称是粉丝。她谈到演员时说：“他是一个有思想的人的性象征。” “他只是一个非常有礼貌的，适当地抚养了，我要说的是孩子……他是一个真正认真对待自己的工作，是一个有趣的伴侣”。</p><p>关于<em>马蒂至高无上的</em>知识，除了有传言称，这是受到专业乒乓球运动员马蒂·雷斯曼（Marty Reisman）的启发，尽管该工作室否认这部电影是基于他的。<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">奥斯卡奖</a>得主帕特洛（Paltrow）在采访中有关这部电影的期望。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHVwe7tJDmY/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="b